Blenny project
Blenny 项目

===What is Blenny?===
===什么是Blenny项目？===

Blenny is an IRC bot to help the Chinese Blender (BlenderCN) to organize, collect useful tips, hints and tuts.
This bot is written by Perl.
Blenny是一个IRC（聊天室）的机器人，用来帮助Blender的中国用户（BlenderCN）整理，收集有用的小经验，提示和教程。
这个机器人是用Perl语言编写的。

===Goals===
===目标===

It's designed as a quick saver for IRC chat user and others. The user can add, search the information really fast.
它是IRC聊天用户和其他用户快速服务通道。用户可以通过它，便捷的添加，查询信息。

===Dream===
===梦想===

We want to give our users a quick, high quality articles about Blender, as free(and the source code) of cause.
我们希望给用户一个快速，高质量的Blender文章服务，当然这些都是免费的（甚至包括源代码本身）。

===How was the name Blenny came from?===
===Blenny的名字怎么来的？===

Blenny came from  Blender, we just cut the -der and added ny for a nice girl-like name.
Blenny的名字来自Blender，我们去掉了der加上了ny，这样名字更女性化，容易被人接纳。

